tags.description: Sandy beach, with a large step up onto the grass of Thompson Field Park.
Sandy beach. Access to Bogue Flats Recreation Area.
tags.name: Bogue Flats Recreation Area

tags.description: Landing in disrepair, next to the ruins of a burnt deck. Near the water, the trail is overgrown. It widens just around the corner. The hill is steep and slippery at points. At the top is a roadside park with parking, pit toilet, picnic tables, and more.
